#: ../../tutorials/io.rst:38
msgid ""
"With one hand, hold your device by the GND pin. Then, with your other "
"hand, touch (or tickle) the 0 (zero) pin. You should see the display "
"change from grumpy to happy!"
msgstr ""
"Jednou rukou drž zariadenie za pin GND. Potom sa druhou rukou dotkni "
"(alebo poštekli) pin 0 (nula). Mal(a) by si vidieť, že displej sa zmení "
